 of the most popular boys' names throughout the medieval period, but less so after the Reformation, though it has continued in regular use to the present day.  Roger, Count of Sicily  (  <i>c.</i>1031–1101 ), son of Tancred, recovered Sicily from the Arabs. His son, also called Roger, ruled Sicily as king, presiding over a court noted for its splendour and patronage of the arts."],"variants":[{"name":"Rodger","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Roger  , in part from the surname derived from the given name in the Middle Ages."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Roger de Mitford was born in 1298 as the son of Adam de Mitford. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1349, at the age of 51."},"et":{"1298–1349":"1298–1349","1325–1357":"1325–1357","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1349":"1349","1325":"1325","1357":"1357","1298":"1298","1275":"1275","1319":"1319"},"fi":{"1298–1349":"1298–1349","1325–1357":"1325–1357","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1349":"1349","1325":"1325","1357":"1357","1298":"1298","1275":"1275","1319":"1319"},"fr":{"1298–1349":"1298–1349","1325–1357":"1325–1357","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1349":"1349","1325":"1325","1357":"1357","1298":"1298","1275":"1275","1319":"1319","lifeSummary":"Roger de Mitford est né en 1298, fils de Adam de Mitford. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1349, à l’âge de 51 ans."},"de":{"1298–1349":"1298–1349","1325–1357":"1325–1357","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1349":"1349","1325":"1325","1357":"1357","1298":"1298","1275":"1275","1319":"1319","lifeSummary":"Roger de Mitford wurde 1298, als Sohn von Adam de Mitford geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1349 im Alter von 51 Jahren."},"ht":{"1298–1349":"1298–1349","1325–1357":"1325–1357","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1349":"1349","1325":"1325","1357":"1357","1298":"1298","1275":"1275","1319":"1319"},"hu":{"1298–1349":"1298–1349","1325–1357":"1325–1357","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1349":"1349","1325":"1325","1357":"1357","1298":"1298","1275":"1275","1319":"1319"},"id":{"1298–1349":"1298–1349","1325–1357":"1325–1357","1